

store order ID on cookie

FRONT END:
  - store order on cookie
    - also add as new order with pending status in database
  - editing cart
    - items added to cookie
      - registered users only: also added to pending order's orderDetails
  - viewing cart
    - order from cookie


BACK END:
  - serializeUser
    - search for any pending order for user
    - append pending order to the cookie
